<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 28.1 (April 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The percentage damage reduction granted from the Avatar Unique Passive on this item has been reduced to 10%, down from 20%.</li><li>The price of this item has been increased to 2990, up from 2835.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26.1 (March 3, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The amount of bonus Magic Resistance and Armor gained Avatar Unique Passive has been reduced to 50% of total Armor and Magic Resistance, down from 100%.</li><li>The duration of the Avatar Unique Passive has been reduced to 3 seconds base, down from 4. The extended duration has also been changed to a max of 6 seconds, down from 8.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The Unique Passive - Divine Intervention II has been removed from this item and replaced with the Unique Passive - Avatar.</li><li>Unique Passive - Avatar: Upon dropping below 50% Health you will gain a bonus Armor, Magic Resistance, and 20% damage reduction for 4 seconds. Dealing damage extends the effect by 1 second up to a maximum of 8 seconds. The bonus values are equal to 100% of your Armor and Magic Resistance. This effect has a 30 second cooldown.</li><li>Price increased to 2835, up from 2430.</li></ul>